      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Surveyors Of the Canadian Pacific\nrailroad are encamped near Trent to-\nday. Stages may be seen from Haus-\nor Junction toward Spokane. The\nsnen say nothing about their plans.\nbut It Is understood that they are\nworking on the branch line Of the\nc. p. r. which Is intended to afford\nthe Canadian road an entrance into\nthe heart Of the Inland Empire."
    }
